welcome_message_body: "Welcome to Singleton, where the stunning landscapes and friendly locals will surely captivate you. Known for its rich history and charming country feel, we invite you to immerse yourself in the city's beauty and experience all it has to offer."

terminals.name: Main Terminal
terminals.description: The main terminal at Singleton Airport serves both domestic and international flights.

terminals.name: Cargo Terminal
terminals.description: The cargo terminal at Singleton Airport handles all air freight and cargo operations.

wifi.note: Free WiFi is available throughout the airport.
